table <I>Geographic Data</I> on page 59 of our 2001 Annual Report and the table
<I>Percentage Change in Geographic Revenues</I> on page 26 of our 2001 Annual Report.
Those tables are incorporated by reference.
</FONT>
<P><FONT size="2">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Our international businesses are subject, in varying degrees, to a number
of risks inherent in carrying on business in other countries. These include
</FONT>
<P>
<TABLE width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
<TR valign="top">
