<P><FONT size="2">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The
effect of product patent expiration or loss also depends upon
</FONT>
<P>
<TABLE width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
