<P><FONT size="2">We promote our products directly through our sales representatives as well as
through advertising.
</FONT>
<P><FONT size="2">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Many other companies, large and small, manufacture and sell one or more
products that are similar to our consumer products. Sources of competitive
advantage include
</FONT>
<P>
